ct]"/><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-186_ pf-heading-2-h3 new-branding-headline-font"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cRmpXP cGRimR pf-188_">Dein ABO-PORTAL</span></h3><p class="sc-hgRQsa gNGIPQ pf-189_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-c526549d-ae2c-4e32-9c32-18f5ccbf0960"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Falls Du etwas an Deinem Spar-Abo ändern möchtest, gelangst Du hier zu Deinem persönlichen Abo-Portal.</span></p><a href="https://stoertebekker.com/a/loop_subscriptions/customer" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button2" class="sc-emIqIH hFkfQE pf-192_">Zum Spar-Abo-Portal</a></div><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-194_ pf-heading-7-h1">Du hast Fragen?</h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-196_ pf-heading-2-h3">LIEFERUNG</h3><div class="sc-gOqwAI jjtufm pf-198_ pf-icon-right" data-scroll-to-top="true" data-open-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3"><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-199_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-200_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="91c9950f-b420-4a0a-8f10-86413794ed97" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Wann wird mein erstes abonniertes Produkt versendet?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-202_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-203_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-204_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-205_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-206_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Deine erste Lieferung erhältst du ganz normal in unserer gewohnten Lieferzeit, also meistens innerhalb von 1-2 Werktagen. Die darauffolgenden Lieferungen erhältst du in dem Rhythmus, den du als Lieferintervall ausgewählt hast.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-208_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-209_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="10864137-94ed-4750-b923-f9da025ed2c8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Werde ich über anstehende Abo-Lieferungen informiert?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-211_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-212_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-213_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-214_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-215_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Wenn Du dein Abo startest, erhältst Du zunächst eine normale Bestellbestätigung passend zu der ersten Bestellung. Kurz bevor deine nächste Abo-Lieferung ansteht, erhältst du eine Erinnerung per Mail und sobald die Lieferung unser Lager verlässt, informieren wir dich ebenfalls per Mail darüber. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-217_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-218_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="23f9da02-5ed2-4872-ace2-071b636fbdfa" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Kann ich das Lieferintervall im Nachhinein ändern?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-220_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-221_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-222_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-223_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-224_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Klar! Wenn du merkst, dass Du Deine Abo-Lieferung doch lieber früher oder später brauchst, kannst Du jederzeit über das Spar-Abo Portal das Lieferintervall deines Abos individuell anpassen.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-226_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-227_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="e2071b63-6fbd-4a92-80da-6e6c061564d4" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l