mn" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-241_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-242_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Das Spar-Abo ist aktuell lediglich in Deutschland verfügbar.  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details></div><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-244_ pf-heading-2-h3">Zahlung</h3><div class="sc-gOqwAI jjtufm pf-246_ pf-icon-right" data-scroll-to-top="true" data-open-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3"><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-247_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-248_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="6098bd7b-d11d-40cb-b47c-850ca15cca62" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Welche Zahlungsarten kann ich für mein Spar-Abo nutzen?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-250_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-251_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-252_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-253_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-254_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Für das Spar-Abo steh die Zahlungsarten PayPal &amp; Kreditkarte, aber auch Google Pay sowie Shop Pay&nbsp; zur Verfügung.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-256_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-257_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="aa0cf6b8-890b-4131-9927-186a481a98c3" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Fallen irgendwelche Gebühren an?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-259_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-260_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-261_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-262_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-263_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Nein! Im Gegenteil - im Abo sicherst Du Dir jederzeit den besten Preis für Dein Produkt.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-265_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-266_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="7c850ca1-5cca-4273-b932-344594831cf9" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Wie oft muss ich zahlen und wann wird mir das Geld berechnet?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-268_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-269_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-270_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-271_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-272_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Deine erste Zahlung wird mit Abschluss des Abonnements fällig. Im Anschluss buchen wir den jeweiligen Betrag automatisch von Deinem PayPal- oder Kreditkartenkonto ab, sobald die nächste Bestellung ausgelöst wird. Du musst Dich somit um nichts kümmern. Sollte es Probleme mit Deiner Zahlung geben, melden wir uns bei Dir per E-Mail.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-274_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-275_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="6bce9ddc-835d-4082-821d-770a85ee6a3d" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Kann ich die Zahlungsart für mein Abo ändern?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-277_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-278_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-279_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-280_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-281_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Klar! Für Abo-Zahlungen stehen Dir die Zahlungsarten PayPal, Kreditkarte, Google Pay sowie Shop Pay zur Verfügung. Du kannst über das Spar-Abo Portal auch andere Konten hinterlegen oder auch die Zahlungsmethode komplett wechseln.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-283_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-284_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="1d770a85-ee6a-4d6d-bb7d-c344567f52a6" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Kann ich Rabattcodes für Abo-Lieferungen nutzen?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-286_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-287_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-288_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-289_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-290_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Rabattcodes sind für die Spar-Abos nicht gültig - Du sicherst Dir jedoch im Abo dauerhaft den besten Preis!  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details></div><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cyRdfs qmQNK pf-292_ pf-heading-2-h3">Flexibilität</h3><div class="sc-gOqwAI jjtufm pf-294_ pf-icon-right" data-scroll-to-top="true" data-open-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3"><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-295_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-296_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="38c78e46-99f1-4221-97c4-60cca446e02f" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Kann ich mein Abo jederzeit kündigen?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-298_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-299_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-300_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-301_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-302_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Ja! Du kannst Dein Abo jederzeit direkt über das Spar-Abo Portal kündigen. Alternativ kannst Du uns natürlich auch eine Mail an <a href="https://mailto:support@stoertebekker.com" target="_self">support@stoertebekker.com</a>&nbsp;schreiben, in der Du die Abo-ID angibst und uns hier mitteilst, dass Du Dein Spar-Abo beenden möchtest. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-304_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-305_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="9647d1ff-51c4-4066-8038-c78e4699f132" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Kann ich mein Abo pausieren?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-307_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-308_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-309_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-310_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-311_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Klar! Du kannst dein Abo jederzeit für bis zu 6 Monate am Stück pausieren und hierbei sogar eine individuell eingestellte Anzahl an Tagen angeben, für die Du Dein Spar-Abo pausieren möchtest.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-313_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-314_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="c460cca4-46e0-4f24-8aed-89376f374950" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Kann ich Abo-Lieferungen überspringen oder verschieben?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-316_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-317_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-318_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-319_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-320_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Ja klar, das ist beides problemlos über das Abo-Portal möglich, damit Du, falls Du mal im Urlaub bist, oder gerade keine Lieferungen entgegennehmen kannst, stets alles so einstellen kannst, dass es für Dich am Besten passt. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-322_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-323_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="251c8568-48e5-428e-bced-6a1a8b344eb8" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Kann ich Produkte innerhalb des Spar-Abos ändern?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-325_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-326_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-327_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-328_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-329_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Ja, das ist kein Problem. Du kannst sowohl die Menge der enthaltenen Produkte sowie die Produkte selbst im Abo jederzeit ändern und tauschen.   </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-331_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-332_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="ed89376f-3749-4083-8525-1c856848e512" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Kann ich ein Spar-Abo buchen und trotzdem einmalige Bestellungen aufgeben?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-334_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-335_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-336_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-337_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-338_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Natürlich! Du kannst ganz normal bestellen, wann immer du möchtest. Das hat keinen Einfluss auf Dein Spar-Abo. Außerdem kannst Du, um Lieferkosten zu sparen, auch Produkte einmalig zu einer Abo-Lieferung hinzufügen. </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-340_ pf-r pf-r-eh pf-sm-hide pf-hide" style="--s-xs:8px;--s-sm:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-341_"><img alt="Marc-schiefer-Logo (2) 1.png__PID:fd8e3732-330f-46b4-9ed0-8879b6749c92" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0317/7116/4804/files/marc-rund.png?v=1763125415&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0317/7116/4804